.SH 版本
.PP
v3.6.1 及以上版本
.SH 示例
.PP
\f[B]示例1：\f[] 将位置集"GuangZhou"设置为集群的 ActiveLocation
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
> var dc = db.getDC()
> dc.setActiveLocation("GuangZhou")
{
  "MatchedNum": 3,
  "SucceedNum": 3,
  "IgnoredNum": 0,
  "FailedNum": 0
}
\f[]
.fi
.PP
\f[B]示例2：\f[] 删除集群的 ActiveLocation
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
> var dc = db.getDC()
> dc.setActiveLocation("")
{
  "MatchedNum": 3,
  "SucceedNum": 3,
  "IgnoredNum": 0,
  "FailedNum": 0
}
\f[]
.fi
.PP
\f[B]示例3：\f[] 仅对指定域的数据组设置 ActiveLocation
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
> var dc = db.getDC()
> dc.setActiveLocation("GuangZhou", {Domain: "mydomain"})
{
  "MatchedNum": 2,
  "SucceedNum": 2,
  "IgnoredNum": 0,
  "FailedNum": 0
}
\f[]
.fi
.PP
\f[B]示例4：\f[] 设置 ActiveLocation 时部分复制组失败的情况
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
> var dc = db.getDC()
> dc.setActiveLocation("Beijing")
{
  "MatchedNum": 4,
  "SucceedNum": 2,
  "IgnoredNum": 0,
  "FailedNum": 2,
  "FailedGroups": ["group3", "group4"]
}
\f[]
.fi
